Package org.autogui.swing

Class GuiSwingKeyBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.autogui.swing.GuiSwingKeyBinding
  • public class GuiSwingKeyBinding
extends Object
    a class for automatic key-stroke assignments. It relies on KeyboardFocusManager which can steel key-events globally.
